    <briefdescription>
<para>The native base class for a setting entry widget for a boolean setting, represented as a checkbox in the UI. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The native base class for a setting entry widget for a boolean setting, represented as a checkbox in the UI.</para>
<para>The widget blueprint implementing this class should be assigned as a value to the SettingEntryWidgetClasses map with the boolean setting definition class (<ref refid="classUSFSettingDefinition__Bool" kindref="compound">USFSettingDefinition_Bool</ref>) as the key in the Developer Settings at Project Settings &gt; Plugins &gt; SettingsFramework. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
